sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Dash as DashboardScreen
    participant EnvHook as useEnvironmentalContext
    participant EnvSvc as environment.js
    participant Location as expo-location
    participant Meteo as Open-Meteo APIs
    participant Prompt as buildInsightPrompt
    participant LlmHook as useLlmInsight
    participant ORClient as openrouter.js
    participant FnClient as functionClient.js
    participant SA as Supabase Auth
    participant Edge as openrouter-insight
    participant OR as OpenRouter

    User->>Dash: Open Dashboard
    Dash->>EnvHook: load()
    EnvHook->>EnvSvc: getEnvironmentalContext()
    EnvSvc->>Location: request permission + current position
    Location-->>EnvSvc: latitude, longitude, place
    par Weather request
        EnvSvc->>Meteo: /forecast
    and Air quality request
        EnvSvc->>Meteo: /air-quality
    end
    Meteo-->>EnvSvc: weather + AQI payloads
    EnvSvc-->>EnvHook: envContext
    EnvHook-->>Dash: location, weather, air data

    Note over Dash: Dashboard already holds the latest physiological state from BLE/model prediction.

    User->>Dash: Tap Generate Insight
    Dash->>Prompt: buildInsightPrompt(envContext, insightEvents)
    Prompt-->>Dash: prompt string
    Dash->>LlmHook: generate(prompt)
    LlmHook->>ORClient: askOpenRouter(system, user)
    ORClient->>FnClient: invokeSupabaseFunction(openrouter-insight)
    FnClient->>SA: getSession()
    SA-->>FnClient: access token
    FnClient->>Edge: POST prompt + x-supabase-auth
    Edge->>SA: getUser(accessToken)
    SA-->>Edge: authenticated user
    Edge->>OR: chat/completions
    OR-->>Edge: assistant content
    Edge-->>FnClient: { content }
    FnClient-->>ORClient: response JSON
    ORClient-->>LlmHook: coaching text
    LlmHook-->>Dash: llmResponse
    Dash-->>User: Coaching message in Coach card
